QUESTION NO: 1
Active Energy Manager (AEM) is provided to our clients for free, but can be upgraded for a cost.
Which one of the following is the advantage to our clients for upgrading?
A. The ability to track the power usage by their systems over time.
B. The ability to establish power caps or power savings
C. The ability to manage the power to the cooling systems in the datacenter based on the heat
being generated by the systems.
D. The ability to power off Intel processors
Answer: B
